                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900526-38-off178 t17900526-38-cd179"></join>, one man's woollen cloth coat, value 8 s. and a boy's ditto, value 10 s. one pair of nankeen breeches, value 4 s. four linen waistcoats, value 5 s. one dimity waistcoat, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17900526-38-victim407" type="victimName">
